text: The Coldtide Fleet are a small principality led by sea baron Prince Kaelisk, with territory just south of the [[Three Sisters]] between [[Stonespur]] and mainland [[Lhazaar Principalities]] in the [[Bitter Sea]]. Kaelisk has recently made a trade deal with House [[Tharashk]] for [[dragonshard]] mining operations in the [[Three Sisters]] islands.
title: Coldtide Fleet
